{"tid":1458342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果大家見到地鐵有壞咗嘅閘機 會唔會唔拍卡就行過去？","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T23:06:51.000Z","uid":10890,"like":59,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"138d8d325a8adcb589a868c8d547566dc19f56f9","tid":1458342,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"如果有朝早 大家去搭地鐵返工嗰陣<br />\n發覺嘅三腳閘機被人搞過嚟<br />\n三隻腳都唔申出嚟 可以直行直過<br />\n新款嗰隻閘機就被人用膠紙膠水痴死哂閂唔埋<br />\n大家會唔會直行直過？<br />\n定係照樣乖乖地拍卡畀錢？<br />\n<br />\n正皮：直行直過！地鐵年年賺咁撚多但啲服務越嚟越閪 點解壞閘我重要畀錢？ <br />\n<br />\n負皮：照畀錢！地鐵壞閘機要拎錢去整，同埋我要做良好公民<br />\n<br />\n純粹想睇下大家心底會點諗<br />\n大家千祈唔好整壞閘機搞到全人類可以直行直過唔畀錢"},{"pid":"85f2d9a32e446db1e59fcc41d5868f2d69f12141","tid":1458342,"uid":49178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2e88d60561624eb98a3b91149811673046fbe0","tid":1458342,"uid":227303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"點出閘"},{"pid":"935522bc6a79ea5b9ae9ff8b8e9f84839c85dc09","tid":1458342,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c2e88d60561624eb98a3b91149811673046fbe0","tid":1458342,"uid":227303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"點出閘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"所以咪叫你唔好整壞啲閘囉"},{"pid":"720b4b0beed6816b2014cb81790f2198ad8c9928","tid":1458342,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"935522bc6a79ea5b9ae9ff8b8e9f84839c85dc09","tid":1458342,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c2e88d60561624eb98a3b91149811673046fbe0","tid":1458342,"uid":227303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"點出閘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"所以咪叫你唔好整壞啲閘囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"咩撚呀，人地問緊冇拍卡入，出要拍卡咁點"},{"pid":"4c99c9106043